en_404823_0	16 more artificial limbs, meant for physically-handicapped civilians of low-income groups in the general area of Iyakachchi, Jaffna were distributed during a brief ceremony at 12 (V) Vijayabahu Infantry Regiment Headquarters under the 55 Division of the Security Force Headquarters - Jaffna (SFHQ-J).
en_404823_1	As has been the practice, Kundasale Centre for Handicapped at the request of the SFHQ-J was generous enough to bear the cost of those limbs.
en_404823_2	Earlier, those sponsors visited the area and picked up those needy handicapped civilians for measurements.
en_404823_3	Presentation of those limbs took place at the VIR Headquarters of the 552 Brigade in the presence of donors and Colonel Dinesh Nanayakkara, 552 Brigade Commander as the Chief Guest.
